{"article_id":"RLcDnuYlvNmr0GlB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Rep. Trey Gowdy is a man under fierce pressure","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"as he leads a congressional Benghazi investigation","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that 's dismissed by Democrats as partisan","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and even questioned by some fellow Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The former prosecutor and three-term South Carolina Republican","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"known for his `` Southern politeness ''","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"is pressing ahead ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"determined to get the facts about the long night of Sept. 11 , 2012 ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"when extremists hit two U.S. facilities in Benghazi , Libya ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and killed four Americans ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"including Ambassador Chris Stevens .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"On Thursday , as chairman of the House Select Committee on Benghazi , faces the star witness in the 17-month , Republican-led investigation","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that already has surpassed the 1970s-era Watergate probe in length .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Hillary Rodham Clinton , secretary of state","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"when the attack happened","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and now a Democratic presidential candidate , will testify in the highly anticipated hearing on Capitol Hill .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"For all the talk","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"of how Clinton used a private email server as secretary ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Gowdy pledged in a recent interview","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that the hearing will be `` Benghazi-centric , ''","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"focused on security before and during the attacks .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Some questions are likely on Clinton 's use of a private email account and server for government business ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Gowdy said ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"but he maintains","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that his approach may `` shock you with fairness . ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Clinton has said","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"the use of a private server was a mistake .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"The 51-year-old Gowdy ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"boyish-looking with close-cropped silver hair ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"has cast himself as a fact-finder","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"as he deals with Republicans","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"eager to portray the attacks as a major national security failure of the Obama administration","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"and Democrats","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"who call the inquiry a pointless partisan exercise after some seven other investigations into the raids .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Gowdy has conducted most of the committee 's work behind closed doors","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"while holding just three public hearings in 17 months , the last one in January .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"The panel has interviewed more than 50 witnesses","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"including seven eyewitnesses","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"hom","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"owdy says","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"ere never questioned by other congressional committees -","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"nd reviewed thousands of documents about security lapses , the military response and the administration 's initial , inaccurate accounts","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"f why the attacks occurred .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"ouse Speaker John Boehner , the driving force behind creation of the committee in May 2014 , said","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"e chose Gowdy , a member of the 2010 tea party class ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"ecause `` he is one of the most professional , capable and respected members of Congress . ''","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"` Time and time again , Trey has proven","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"hat he is the best person","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"o ensure","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"he American people know the truth","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"bout what happened in Benghazi , ''","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"oehner , R-Ohio , told The Associated Press in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"emocrats counter","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"hat the $ 4.5 million inquiry is a costly partisan hunt","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"o destroy Clinton 's White House bid","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"nd complain","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"hat they have been frozen out of some of the committee interviews .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"hey point to the recent comments of two Republicans","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"ho suggested","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"linton is the panel 's target .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"ouse Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy , R-Calif. , said last month","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"hat the committee can take credit for Clinton 's diminished public standing in recent months , a comment","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"e later retracted .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"n Wednesday , Rep. Richard Hanna , R-N.Y. ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"ho is not on the committee ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"aid","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"` a big part '' of the Benghazi investigation was designed","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"o go after Clinton .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"` At this point , Trey Gowdy 's inquiry has zero credibility left , ''","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"aid Clinton spokesman Brian Fallon .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"linton called the panel an `` arm of the Republican National Committee . ''","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"former Republican staffer recently said","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"e was unlawfully fired","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"n part","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"ecause he sought a comprehensive probe into the attacks","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"nstead of focusing on Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"ir Force Reserve Maj. Bradley Podliska also complained","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"hat the committee was engaged in social activities such as an informal wine club","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"icknamed `` Wine Wednesdays . ''","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"owdy said","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"odliska was fired","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"or mishandling classified information and other mistakes .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"till , the chairman felt compelled to issue a statement","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"aying","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"is panel `` is not focused on Secretary Clinton ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"nd to the extent we have given any attention to Clinton ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"t is because she was secretary of state at all relevant times","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"overed by this committee 's jurisdiction . ''","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"hatever criticism , Gowdy is acutely aware","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"hat Thursday 's hearing is likely to be the committee 's make-or-break moment ,","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"here he can revive its credibility","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"r see it widely discredited .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"epublicans blame Democrats for the partisan breakdown","depth":3},{"id":93,"text":"nd say","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"owdy has been patient with the administration","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"s he seeks documents from the State Department and other agencies .","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"` He 's a lot more patient","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"han I would have been , ''","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"aid Rep. Mike Pompeo , R-Kan. , a member of the committee .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"owdy is `` bending over backward '' for Democrats","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"ho `` have not lifted one finger","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"o help us in the fact-discovery process , ''","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"ompeo said .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"ep. Adam Smith , D-Wash. , said","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"e believes","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"owdy was sincere in","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"` saying from the beginning","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"hat he wanted to do this right .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"ut it just has n't happened .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"t has not played out the way","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"hat Rep. Gowdy said","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"t would . ''","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"efore the fierce partisanship , Gowdy allowed Smith to participate in a hearing via Skype","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"fter the congressman was sidelined by surgery .","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"nother panel member , Rep. Adam Schiff , D-Calif. , said","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"owdy `` is under immense pressure '' from his party","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"o deliver something after 17 months .","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"chiff ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"ho has called for the committee to be disbanded ,","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"aid","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"e likes Gowdy ,","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"ut `` the intense and partisan focus of the committee on Secretary Clinton above all else has made our work on the committee difficult ,","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"o say the least . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":245,"left":214,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":149,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":126,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":0,"right":125,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":1,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":132,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":128,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":7,"right":130,"relation":"elab